Definition: a bevel gear that permits rotation of two shafts at different speeds
Example: used on the rear axle of automobiles to allow wheels to rotate at different speeds on curves
Synonyms: differential, bevel_gear, a, bevel, gear, that, permits, rotation, of, two, shafts, at, different, speeds, used, on, the, rear, axle, automobiles, to, allow, wheels, rotate, curves
Category: noun.artifact
